      "content": "The main reason for the change is to minimize the risk of any automated hallucinations or logic errors making it into the final filing. We feel that having a human lawyer verify every single piece of reasoning is a safer way to ensure the firm's accuracy than relying on the model's direct output. We'll let you know when the new search protocols are ready.",
